DESCRIPTION:\n\n\n\nCome one\, come all! Finals are inevitably among us an
 d so is the inevitable necessity for everyone's favorite study time\, str
 ess induced pick-me-up . . . . . Chick-Fil-A! Finals are often the most s
 tressful time of the year for first-year (and every other year) students\
 , and one of the best ways to destress\, at least in my experience\, is f
 ood. RHA will provide pre-packaged Chick-Fil-A meals containing chicken s
 andwiches\, chips\, and a cookie/brownie in addition to bottles of water.
 \n\n\n\n\n\nHosted by: Residence Hall Association\n\nAdditional Informati
 on can be found at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12450992
