DESCRIPTION:This is our general meeting for all members. Typically\, durin
 g general meetings we will discuss specific writing techniques\, guide me
 mbers towards writing resources\, provide prompts\, share works\, and mor
 e! During select general meetings\, we may also bring in guest speakers o
 r host special events related to writing and the writing industry.\n \nWr
 iters Place also offers weekly fiction and poetry workshops and publishes
  our own yearly lit journal. Reach out if you're interested!\n \nNew memb
 ers or first-time attendees are always welcome!\n\nHosted by: Writers Pla
 ce\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: https://beinvolved.indiana.
 edu/event/12438872
