DESCRIPTION:Generation One Initiative is designating Thursday April 28\, 2
 026 as our networking event with previous IU alumni from various career s
 ectors that are looking to share with college students about topics inclu
 ding: the pathway as being a first-generation/low-income individuals\, ad
 vice on success in college\, the transitional experience from secondary e
 ducation to full-time work experience\, and what are some key measures to
  balance work-social life balance. It will include the open networking af
 ter the panel and alumni discussion of the event.\n\nHosted by: First Gen
 eration and Limited/Low-Income Programs\n\nAdditional Information can be 
 found at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12410683
