 raduation Stoles and share our memories with our favorite Grads. This eve
 nt is open to everyone and will be a way to support our students. You don
 't have to be a grad to attend. \nSee you from 12 pm-2 pm\nF.Y.I. You hav
 e to attend to receive a First Gen Graduation Stole: If you need the RSVP
  link\, email Jamartae Jackson(jj295@iu.edu)\n\nHosted by: First Generati
 on and Limited/Low-Income Programs\n\nAdditional Information can be found
  at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12413016
